quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"We have indeed sent down the Qur’an in the Night of Destiny."
  97,2,"And what have you understood, what the Night of Destiny is!"
  97,3,"The Night of Destiny is better than a thousand months."
  97,4,"In it descend the angels and Jibreel, by the command of their Lord – for all works."
  97,5,"It is peace until the rising of dawn."
